Package org.opensocial.models

Class Summary
Activity OpenSocial model class representing an activity.
Album OpenSocial model class representing an album, a collection of media items.
AppData OpenSocial model class representing AppData, uninterpreted key/value pairs.
Group OpenSocial model class representing a group, which is used to tag or categorize people and their relationships.
MediaItem OpenSocial model class representing a media item (image, movie, or audio).
Model Generic OpenSocial model class.
Person OpenSocial model class representing a person/user.
